OL,3,CDomino's takes on restaurant rivals
OL,4,Cwith new range of thinner pizzas
OL,6,FDomino's is rolling out thinner pizzas
OL,7,Fin a new Italian-inspired range it
OL,8,Fhopes will buy a slice of the more
OL,9,Fpremium market and cater to new
OL,10,Fcustomers.
OL,12,FThe takeaway firm said it was
OL,13,Fresponding to increasing demand for a
OL,14,F"restaurant experience at home".
OL,16,FThe new "Italiano's" pizza range will
OL,17,Ffeature five pizzas with a thinner-
OL,18,Fstyle crust and Italian-inspired
OL,19,Ftoppings including nduja, goat's
OL,20,Fcheese and a pesto drizzle.
