OL,3,CDomino's takes on restaurant rivals
OL,4,Cwith new range of thinner pizzas
OL,6,FDomino's, which is known for being
OL,7,Fpopular among students and younger
OL,8,Fpeople, said bringing a different
OL,9,Fstyle of pizza to its menu responds to
OL,10,Fgrowing demand for at-home takeaway
OL,11,Foccasions.
OL,13,FChief executive Nicola Frampton said:
OL,14,F"We're seeing that for certain
OL,15,Foccasions, whether that's a date night
OL,16,For a relaxed evening in, people are
OL,17,Fincreasingly looking for something
OL,18,Fthat feels a bit more like a
OL,19,Frestaurant experience at home, and
OL,20,Fthis range allows us to tap into those
OL,21,Fmoments."
