OL,3,CDomino's takes on restaurant rivals
OL,4,Cwith new range of thinner pizzas
OL,6,FThe launch comes after restaurant
OL,7,Fchain Pizza Express has continued to
OL,8,Fexpand its Romana pizza menu, a
OL,9,Fthinner and crispier version of the
OL,10,Fclassic pizza that sells for a higher
OL,11,Fprice.
OL,13,FIt also sells a range of its branded
OL,14,Fpizzas in supermarkets to cater to
OL,15,Fpeople eating out less frequently and
OL,16,Flooking to upgrade meals at home.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
