OL,3,CDomino's takes on restaurant rivals
OL,4,Cwith new range of thinner pizzas
OL,6,FMeanwhile, newer pizzerias like
OL,7,Fsourdough pizza chain Franco Manca
OL,8,Fhave grown rapidly, having been
OL,9,Ffounded in 2008 and now running about
OL,10,F70 restaurants across the UK.
OL,12,FOn the other hand, takeaway and eat-in
OL,13,Fchain Pizza Hut has struggled against
OL,14,Fan under-pressure casual dining
OL,15,Fsector, and around half its
OL,16,Frestaurants were shut down last year
OL,17,Fafter falling into administration.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
