OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776038571
OL,3,CDomino's takes on restaurant rivals
OL,4,Cwith new range of thinner pizzas
OL,6,FDomino's has said it wants to expand
OL,7,Fits pizza offering and customer base,
OL,8,Fafter reporting a slight decline in
OL,9,Forder numbers last year.
OL,11,FMs Frampton said the Italiano's range
OL,12,Fwas a "strong example of how we're
OL,13,Fcontinuing to evolve and broaden our
OL,14,Fpizza offering, attract new customers
OL,15,Fand unlock new occasions for growth".
